{"tid":1289624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求未達成前絕對不能談判","createTime":"2019-07-06T07:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T11:28:05.000Z","uid":52200,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8e10e0869f54abd7b06b5e1ca25730bb794f9d8","tid":1289624,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZK1hpDrSQ9M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZK1hpDrSQ9M&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=1f16a4f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZK1hpDrSQ9M</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1 &bull; 全面撤回送中惡法 <br />\n2 &bull; 反對定性暴動 <br />\n3 &bull; 釋放抗爭者 撤銷所有控罪 <br />\n4 &bull; 追究濫權警察暴行 <br />\n5 &bull; 林鄭下台，立即實行雙普選</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n冷血啲咁講，真正令果一班狗官願意妥協嘅唔係人數，更加唔係人命，班狗官真正怕嘅係Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act，真正怕嘅係美國製裁，真正怕嘅係自己同屋企人嘅外國護照俾人吊燒，呢點完全係唔燒到埋身就唔理嘅仆街心態，最根本嘅原因係因為佢哋唔需要面對選民，唔需要向人民負責，基本上嚟講，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">係過往</span></span>，佢哋做咩都係冇成本架，甚至乎殺人。<br />\n<br />\n我再重申：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">狗官們怕嘅係Human Rights Act，怕嘅係國際制裁。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何人只要遭到美國製裁，所有係美國有生意嘅公司嘅公司都必須同該等人士斷絕來往(包括間接性質)，換言之，Human Rights and Democracy Act通過後，鄭匪與一眾狗官只能共享大灣區榮耀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">接下來嘅日子，我哋必須繼續向國際社會說明，香港人權狀況仍然受到港共政權打壓。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果香港人，係呢個時候妥協，只會出現以下呢個情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：外國媒體<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：Trump<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：鄭匪月娥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：與各界人士會面後，特區政府充分了解民意，接下來，特區政府會加把勁做好民生工作同青年工作，盡快讓社會重回正軌，特區政府會繼續虛心聆聽各界人士意見。特區政府與各界人士的對話亦充分反映一國兩制的落實，以及中央政府對特區的支持。對於國際社會指責香港人權狀況倒退，完全係無稽之談。香港市民仍然依照基本法享有和平集會嘅權利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：After meeting protesters and students representatives, the Hong Kong Government and Hong Kong People have reached a consensus that the society has to restore peace and order. Political issue should be put aside.  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：I told you. Hong Kong people could resolve the issue themselves, and they really did a great job<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後香港人繼續翻工，本應為事件負責嘅人繼續發大財，食人血饅頭。"},{"pid":"e8c7ebfe368a2ad16c2061b723c902fb3c6ad2d2","tid":1289624,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"香港公民社會嘅發展，一輸就輸十年。<br />\n<br />\n一輸就係成個千禧年代嘅人都輪晒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">絕不妥協，絕不談判！</span>"},{"pid":"7570927b0c88027bcaa3e004cf59fe0c26ced873","tid":1289624,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:42:34.000Z","msg":"邊個贊成傾，去傾都係鬼"},{"pid":"35db9a5adecdff61f8f3edb7363afc76050bad92","tid":1289624,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"假如有一天，香港成為大灣區，我哋都要林鄭及其子孫一世留係大灣區！"},{"pid":"707efcd23bf44b71e06b206dbac33cbe3d78156c","tid":1289624,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"依家去談判，絕對係自毀城牆。<br />\n依家去妥協，國際社會就會認為問題解決。"},{"pid":"51dca226b21ca5f1b492162670a3c280bc69a3ff","tid":1289624,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:48:10.000Z","msg":"香港人必須堅持下去，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">直至林鄭遭到制裁！</span></span>"},{"pid":"13aa9eadd5a6b6c62585deed6e83b012fde633a0","tid":1289624,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:51:36.000Z","msg":"民意係好清楚。無談判嘅空間！"},{"pid":"ab8f80c5e59eeede51359f089444f15f8119a9d3","tid":1289624,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"李家超：新彊反恐工作值得香港參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1289170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1289170</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢班狗官全部都係共產黨爪牙，佢哋想係香港起集中營啊！<br />\n<br />\n談判、妥協只會令到佢哋避過制裁！"},{"pid":"2e6413efc27e1f0eaf42594e844f91230c4608da","tid":1289624,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:58:32.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6b37eb223574b8223ae0784fc31b7361e55e3a","tid":1289624,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"係成功之前，我哋必須堅持下去，要持續向港共政權施壓！"